    GTextPane

    public static class GTextPane.MemoryFixedHTMLEditorKit
extends HTMLEditorKit
    The HTMLEditorKit used for working around Java bug 6406218. Use GTextPane.initializeWorkAroundJavaBug6406218() instead of using this class directly. This class is only public because Java requires it to be public for the bug fix to work.
